PN,41901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780427467
OL,3,C300 water voles released back into
OL,4,CRiver Wey in Surrey
OL,6,FAround 300 water voles have been
OL,7,Freintroduced into the River Wey in
OL,8,FSurrey to help restore the species.
OL,10,FThey were released by the National
OL,11,FTrust and partners, into the North Wey
OL,12,Fbetween Farnham and Froyle.
OL,14,FIt's the second in a series of planned
OL,15,Freleases across the 87mile catchment,
OL,16,Fwhich aims to see the species make a
OL,17,Frecovery at a landscape level.
OL,19,FFurther waves of releases will happen
OL,20,Fover the following 12 months.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
