FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780427467
OL,3,C300 water voles released back into
OL,4,CRiver Wey in Surrey
OL,6,FThe plan is to restore a sustainable
OL,7,Fpopulation of water voles, all the way
OL,8,Ffrom the source of the River Wey on
OL,9,FBlack Down in the South Downs National
OL,10,FPark, to Weybridge on the River Thames.
OL,12,FThe water vole was threatened with
OL,13,Fhabitat loss and predation drove them
OL,14,Falmost to the verge of extinction in
OL,15,FBritain's rivers.
OL,17,FNow it is returning to the River Wey
OL,18,Fcatchment in Surrey, Sussex and
OL,19,FHampshire, having been declared
OL,20,Flocally extinct.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780427467
OL,3,C300 water voles released back into
OL,4,CRiver Wey in Surrey
OL,6,FThe project covers an area of over
OL,7,F1000 square kilometres, roughly
OL,8,Fequivalent to 2.5 times the size of
OL,9,Fthe Isle of Wight.
OL,11,FIt's been made possible due to
OL,12,Fpartnership of local people,
OL,13,Flandowners and organisations, led by
OL,14,Fthe National Trust's South Downs
OL,15,Fcountryside team, the Environment
OL,16,FAgency, the River Wey Trust, the South
OL,17,FEast Rivers Trust and Derek Gow
OL,18,FConsultancy.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780427467
OL,3,C300 water voles released back into
OL,4,CRiver Wey in Surrey
OL,6,FDavid Elliott, National Trust Lead
OL,7,FRanger for the South Downs West said:
OL,8,F"Water voles have been locally extinct
OL,9,Fhere for more than 20 years.
OL,11,F"But today we are bringing them back
OL,12,Fto the North Wey, right here in
OL,13,FFarnham Town Centre.
OL,15,F"This wonderful little animal is
OL,16,Fmaking a come back and we couldn't be
OL,17,Fmore delighted than to share that with
OL,18,Fthe people of Farnham.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780427467
OL,3,C300 water voles released back into
OL,4,CRiver Wey in Surrey
OL,6,F"We live in a time of wildlife and
OL,7,Fnature crisis, but we represent a
OL,8,Fgroup of people who are not prepared
OL,9,Fto accept that outcome.
OL,11,F"We are here to represent the work of
OL,12,Fhundreds of people across this river
OL,13,Fcatchment who have come together to do
OL,14,Fsomething positive about bringing
OL,15,Fnature and wildlife back to this
OL,16,Fbeautiful river.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780427467
OL,3,C300 water voles released back into
OL,4,CRiver Wey in Surrey
OL,6,F"The water vole is a species that used
OL,7,Fto be common. The disappearance of the
OL,8,Frare is what often grabs people's
OL,9,Fattention, but the disappearance of
OL,10,Fthe common is what we should all care
OL,11,Fabout."
OL,13,FThe work has been funded by the
OL,14,FNational Trust, the Environment
OL,15,FAgency's Water Environment Improvement
OL,16,FFund and the Black Down and Hindhead
OL,17,FSupporters of the National Trust.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780427467
OL,3,C300 water voles released back into
OL,4,CRiver Wey in Surrey
OL,6,FThe first stage of the project saw
OL,7,Fwater vole releases took place in
OL,8,FAugust 2025, in the upper reaches of
OL,9,Fthe River Wey between Haslemere and
OL,10,FHeadley.
OL,12,FSurveys this spring confirmed that
OL,13,Fthese initial populations have
OL,14,Festablished successfully.
OL,16,FAlongside evidence of their bank-side
OL,17,Fburrows and feeding signs, the return
OL,18,Fof the species has been confirmed by
OL,19,FeDNA water sample testing ` and photos
OL,20,Ffrom remote movement-sensor cameras.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780427467
OL,3,C300 water voles released back into
OL,4,CRiver Wey in Surrey
OL,6,FWater voles play an important role in
OL,7,Fthe biodiversity of riverside
OL,8,Fecosystems.
OL,10,FThey are a source of food for
OL,11,Fstruggling predators like barn owls
OL,12,Fand otters. Where they graze on
OL,13,Fgrasses and rushes, they help reshape
OL,14,Fhabitats and create space for rare
OL,15,Fplants to grow.
OL,17,FYet during the course of the 20th
OL,18,Fcentury, the population of the water
OL,19,Fvole in England declined by 93% and
OL,20,Fhas been in further rapid decline
OL,21,Fsince 2000.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780427467
OL,3,C300 water voles released back into
OL,4,CRiver Wey in Surrey
OL,6,FPaul Davy, Environment Agency
OL,7,FCatchment Coordinator for the River
OL,8,FWey, said: "We were keen to support
OL,9,Fthis vital project and help re-
OL,10,Festablish the water vole, a much-loved
OL,11,Fnative species and ecosystem engineer
OL,12,Fthat has been absent from the Wey
OL,13,Fcatchment for many years.
OL,15,F"This project has been a fantastic
OL,16,Fexample of a catchment-based approach
OL,17,Fand effective partnership working.
OL,26,@pD@LOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780427467
OL,3,C300 water voles released back into
OL,4,CRiver Wey in Surrey
OL,6,F"In addition to providing funding, the
OL,7,FEnvironment Agency has helped the
OL,8,FNational Trust establish the network
OL,9,Fby drawing on our local knowledge and
OL,10,Fbroad network of contacts within the
OL,11,Fcatchment."
OL,13,FLocal volunteer and Farnham resident
OL,14,FLibby Ralph, has played a key role in
OL,15,Fthe project. She said: "I remember
OL,16,Fstill seeing water voles in the 1980s,
OL,17,Fand as for everyone, they gradually
OL,18,Fdisappeared without us realising.
OL,26,@sD@KO]wD@XOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780427467
OL,3,C300 water voles released back into
OL,4,CRiver Wey in Surrey
OL,6,F"Then in 2014/15 I helped with a
OL,7,Fcounty-wide survey where we searched
OL,8,Fdiligently, but very sadly concluded
OL,9,Fthat water voles were functionally
OL,10,Fextinct in Surrey. I have hoped since
OL,11,Fthat moment that one day we'd be able
OL,12,Fto return them to the River Wey.
OL,14,F"They are such iconic animals, and
OL,15,Fmany people have a soft spot for them,
OL,16,Foften through the 'Wind in the
OL,17,FWillows' connection.
OL,19,F"It has been inspiring to be part of
OL,20,Fthis project and realising how many
OL,21,Fmore people are enthused by it.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780427467
OL,3,C300 water voles released back into
OL,4,CRiver Wey in Surrey
OL,6,F"All the landowners and organisations
OL,7,Fthat have played a part are a
OL,8,Fwonderful community, and I hope this
OL,9,Flays the foundation for many more
OL,10,Factions for wildlife in our wonderful
OL,11,Friver corridor."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,26,@sD@PO]
